p.flow-text.
  I plan on coming out with a third version, which will feature a different art style and more of an open world field. I am bringing in an artist and a programmer to help me with the project, which hopefully should make development faster. I am using the #[a(href='https://strangeioc.github.io/strangeioc/') StrangeIOC] framework to develop the new version since I am a fan of dependency injection and MVC style programming, and from my experience it seems to do a good job at decoupling code, which I sometimes find difficult with the AdHoc nature Unity's component system. Finally, I want to give a shutout to #[a(href='http://coreyhoard.com/') Corey Hoard] for aiding me with astrophysics and computer graphics sorcery from time to time over the course of the project.
